#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/colour_correction/rgb_adjustment.rst:18
msgid ""
"This filter is for simple manual color adjustment by RGB channel, either "
"through adding constants, or changing the channel gammas or gains."
msgstr ""
"Aquest filtre serveix per a un senzill ajust manual del color per al canal "
"RGB, ja sigui afegint constants o canviant les gammes o els guanys del canal."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/effect_groups/colour_correction/rgb_adjustment.rst:20
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Simple` means that it works channel-wise, no crosstalk. The "
"off-diagonal elements of the transform matrix are zero - no color crosstalk, "
"no color space rotation. But this should be sufficient for many tasks. For "
"example, when shooting under tungsten light, the blue signal will not "
"migrate into red, it will simply be too small. Amplifying the blue (and a "
"bit of green too) should be all that is needed. Similar, an underwater shot "
"will simply be red deficient, needing some red boost, etc."
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`Senzill` significa que funciona segons el canal, sense "
"diafonia. Els elements fora de la diagonal de la matriu de transformació són "
"zero: no hi ha diafonia de color, ni gir de l'espai de color. Però això "
"hauria de ser suficient per a moltes tasques. Per exemple, quan es dispara "
"sota llum de tungstè, el senyal blau no migrarà al vermell, senzillament "
"serà massa petit. Amplificar el blau (i també una mica de verd) hauria de "
"ser tot el que cal. De la mateixa manera, disparar sota l'aigua senzillament "
"serà deficient de vermell, necessitarà una mica de relleu, etc."

